stories.title: Afridi inspires emphatic win
stories.subTitle: Pakistan v Kenya, Edgbaston, Pool C
stories.summary: Shahid Afridi's quickish legbreaks bamboozled the Kenyan batsmen, and set up a simple seven-wicket win for a markedly superior Pakistan side

stories.title: Same time tomorrow
stories.subTitle: Kenya v Pakistan, Edgbaston, Pool C
stories.summary: It was cold, windy and drizzling at Edgbaston, and there were few complaints when Pakistan's match with Kenya was called off for the day
